---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../../components/Hero.astro";
import ServiceCard from "../../components/ServiceCard.astro";
import CtaBand from "../../components/CtaBand.astro";
import { services } from "../../data/business";

const seo = {
  title: "Services | Countertops & Cabinets in Melbourne, FL | Mayan Stonecrafters",
  description:
    "Mayan Stonecrafters provides countertop, cabinet, flooring & tile services in Melbourne, FL. Personalized solutions. Call us at (321) 821-4381.",
  keywords:
    "countertop services Melbourne FL, cabinet services, flooring, bathroom remodeling, countertop installation, countertop fabrication, granite installation, tile collections, stone services Brevard County, Mayan Stonecrafters",
  path: "/services/",
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <Hero eyebrow="Creative Options, Personalized Solutions" title="Services" compact={true} />

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16">
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-charcoal/85">
      Here at Mayan Stonecrafters, Inc., we pride ourselves on coming up with innovative ideas that
      let us better serve our clients. We're problem-solvers, innovators, and offer a complete range
      of services designed to meet the various needs and wants of a diverse clientele. Our extensive
      skills and industry knowledge offer our clients the ability to bring their unique visions to
      life. At every turn, we strive to personalize our services, tailoring the experience according
      to the specifications of the client. It's what we'd want from a boutique establishment such as
      ourselves, and it's what you should expect too.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl">No-Obligation Consultation</h2>
        <div class="mt-3 h-1 w-16 bg-accent"></div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-charcoal/85">
          For us, the sooner we prove our worth, the better. That's why we offer a no-obligation
          consultation service: so that we can demonstrate the value of our services for ourselves.
          It's a chance for our clients to learn about us, discover the quality of our work, and
          experience our services first-hand - all without having to worry about getting locked into a
          hard-and-fast contract. We don't feel the need to pressure our clients into anything. After
          your consultation, you're free to walk away. Risk-free.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl">Fast Response</h2>
        <div class="mt-3 h-1 w-16 bg-accent"></div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-charcoal/85">
          Speed is key in any industry, and ours is no exception. With that in mind, we are proud to
          offer our clients swift service and rapid response times. We harness efficient
          organizational practices to keep a lean business model, cutting red tape everywhere we see
          it. The result? Superior service, better customer support, and less stress and fewer
          headaches for you. Here at Mayan Stonecrafters, Inc., we're not just fast. We're
          lightning-fast.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-stone-soft/40 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl">What We Offer</h2>
      <div class="accent-bar mt-4 h-1 w-24 bg-accent"></div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {services.map((s) => <ServiceCard title={s.title} href={`/services/${s.slug}/`} />)}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand heading="Call Us Now!" text="Reach us to get started today!" />
</BaseLayout>
